    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.4.11-12"/>
                <note type="curatorial">11</note>
                <note type="curatorial">#2 Fink Collection</note>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Jan 20. 1923
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Daddy</salute>
                </opener>
                
                <p>How are you?</p> 
                <p>We are having a hard rain today.</p> 
                <p>Our pupy is fine.</p> 
                <p>I see now that I can not get along with all these women.</p> 
                <p>When I write you another letter Bessie will probably have a calf.</p> 
                <p>Will you have the pig buchere I when you come back.</p> 
                <p>The Franklin bay came and got too books.</p> 
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.4.11-12"/>
                <note type="curatorial">12</note>
                
                <p>He took Hurricane williams and THe. dead command.</p> 
                <closer>
                    <salute>Love and Bushels of Kisses</salute> 
                    <signed>from Sig.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
            
        </body>
        
